00:26:42.902 --> 00:26:44.467
Utility room?
Supply room?


293
00:26:44.467 --> 00:26:45.682
Store room? Anything.

294
00:26:45.682 --> 00:26:47.246
He can't tell
the difference.


295
00:26:47.246 --> 00:26:49.331
Put someone
in here who can.


296
00:27:05.450 --> 00:27:07.015
<i>There's a game out there,</i>

