00:27:41.467 --> 00:27:43.379
Bets down.

310
00:27:44.899 --> 00:27:46.333
How'd you learn that?

311
00:27:46.333 --> 00:27:48.896
I used to do it
at weddings.


312
00:27:48.896 --> 00:27:50.461
Hey, can you do
card tricks, too?


313
00:27:50.982 --> 00:27:51.982
Sure.

314
00:27:56.152 --> 00:27:58.238
Cards to the gamblers.

