He's all right.


362
00:29:46.852 --> 00:29:48.764
Come on, boys.
On your feet.


363
00:29:48.764 --> 00:29:50.329
We've got to make
that train.


364
00:29:50.329 --> 00:29:51.371
Are you going with us?

365
00:29:51.892 --> 00:29:54.369
Of course. I've got
lots of trains to handle.


366
00:29:54.369 --> 00:29:55.976
Lots of dead men.

