00:30:42.506 --> 00:30:44.592
<i>Help me.</i>

374
00:30:44.592 --> 00:30:48.764
<i>Don't let them
cut my legs off.</i>


375
00:30:48.764 --> 00:30:52.934
<i>Don't let them take my legs, too.</i>

