Merry Christmas.
We must have a just


1251
01:24:45.940 --> 01:24:49.068
and lasting peace!

1252
01:24:49.068 --> 01:24:51.153
Merry Christmas.
We've already got ours.


1253
01:24:51.153 --> 01:24:52.196
Damn right.

1254
01:24:52.196 --> 01:24:54.282
See these?
Two arms.


1255
01:24:54.282 --> 01:24:55.845
Merry Christmas.
You see these?


1256
01:24:55.845 --> 01:24:56.888
Two legs.

1257
