Liberty.
I love you, Kareen.


1266
01:25:11.486 --> 01:25:14.614
Merry Christmas.
You're so lucky, Joe. You are.


1267
01:25:14.614 --> 01:25:15.613
You don't understand.

1268
01:25:15.613 --> 01:25:17.699
I have to make
the world safe.


1269
01:25:18.220 --> 01:25:19.785
This is champagne.

1270
01:25:19.785 --> 01:25:21.826
Merry Christmas.

1271
01:25:21.826 --> 01:25:22.868
I'm the boss.

1272
01:25:22.868 --> 01:25:24.954
This is champagne.

1273
01:25:24.954 --> 01:25:27.561
Merry Christmas.

1274
01:25:27.561 --> 01:25:28.604
I'm the boss.
You're not my boy.


1275
01:25:29.125 --> 01:25:30.167
This is champagne.

1276
01:25:30.167 --> 01:25:31.210
Where's my boy?

1277
01:25:31.210 --> 01:25:33.296
Merry Christmas.
Kareen?


1278
01:25:33.296 --> 01:25:35.381
Where's
my little boy?


1279
01:25:35.381 --> 01:25:36.424
Kareen?

1280
01:25:36.424 --> 01:25:38.510
I'm the boss.

1281
