This is champagne.

1282
01:25:40.073 --> 01:25:43.071
Merry Christmas!

1283
01:25:44.548 --> 01:25:46.547
Fellow workers.

1284
01:25:48.154 --> 01:25:49.067
Ahem!

1285
01:25:49.588 --> 01:25:51.109
Fellow workers?

1286
01:25:53.065 --> 01:25:54.454
Fellow workers!

1287
01:25:58.104 --> 01:26:00.711
Due to the war emergency,

1288
01:26:00.711 --> 01:26:04.403
our little holiday will end
in just three more minutes.


1289
01:26:04.403 --> 01:26:06.923
But the ovens are hot,

1290
01:26:06.923 --> 01:26:09.183
and we must keep
the home fires burning.


1291
01:26:10.530 --> 01:26:11.572
Let us sing.

1292
01:26:15.222 --> 01:26:21.696
